column1: completed emails

Chris Jones,

I hope this email finds you well. I'm a researcher with Govpack, an open-source technology that aggregates data on state- and local-level elected officials, allowing local newspapers to easily build candidate profiles and election guides. I'm in the process of data collection, and I wanted to make sure that I have complete, accurate data to fill out your profile.

This is the information I've collected:
• Name: Chris Jones
• Party: Democratic Party
• State: AR
• Status: Challenger
• Office: Governor of Arkansas

• Image: https://blackconsumernews.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/Dr.ChrisJones-scaled.jpg
• Campaign Website: https://chrisforgovernor.com/
• Campaign Address: P.O. Box 242046 Little Rock, AR 72223
• Personal Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/cmjones99
• Campaign Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/jonesforAR
• Campaign Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC001wEeDS9P1Fpj__CQH9bQ/featured
• Personal Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/cmjones99/
• Campaign Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jonesforAR/
